Message.SourceString: You must be the newbie. I'm Zanik, it's a pleasure to meet you.
Message.LocalizedString: You must be the newbie. I'm Zanik, it's a pleasure to meet you.

Message.SourceString: Hi there. It's good to see new blood, hope you're ready to brave this place. I think Doric needs your attention, best say hi.
Message.LocalizedString: Hi there. It's good to see new blood, hope you're ready to brave this place. I think Doric needs your attention, best say hi.

Message.SourceString: When you've done all that come back and see me. I'll give you something to help you on your journey.
Message.LocalizedString: When you've done all that come back and see me. I'll give you something to help you on your journey.

Message.SourceString: Then make and claim a bed to rest in. To make a bed you're going to need something soft, like fur. Look around for small creatures to get fur from.
Message.LocalizedString: Then make and claim a bed to rest in. To make a bed you're going to need something soft, like fur. Look around for small creatures to get fur from.

Message.SourceString: I see you've got yourself all set up now, great work!
Message.LocalizedString: I see you've got yourself all set up now, great work!

Message.SourceString: Ashenfall's a harsh place to live in, you're gonna need a shelter and somewhere to rest.
Message.LocalizedString: Ashenfall's a harsh place to live in, you're gonna need a shelter and somewhere to rest.

Message.SourceString: Make yourself a shelter out of wood and stone. Any building will do, just needs floors, walls and a roof. When building, be sure to keep your structure stable.
Message.LocalizedString: Make yourself a shelter out of wood and stone. Any building will do, just needs floors, walls and a roof. When building, be sure to keep your structure stable.

Message.SourceString: Why not expand your shelter and turn it into a proper home? You could add rooms, floors, really make something of it.
Message.LocalizedString: Why not expand your shelter and turn it into a proper home? You could add rooms, floors, really make something of it.

Message.SourceString: Not finished yet? Once you've made a shelter, make sure you've claimed a bed. Then come back and see me.
Message.LocalizedString: Not finished yet? Once you've made a shelter, make sure you've claimed a bed. Then come back and see me.

Message.SourceString: I imagine you've been seeing your skills grow stronger. As you level up, you'll unlock special spells to make surviving here easier.
Message.LocalizedString: I imagine you've been seeing your skills grow stronger. As you level up, you'll unlock special spells to make surviving here easier.

Message.SourceString: To cast spells you're going to need to learn about runes. The Wise Old Man can help you with that.
Message.LocalizedString: To cast spells you're going to need to learn about runes. The Wise Old Man can help you with that.

Message.SourceString: Death's made a deal with the Wise Old Coot, so if you die you'll just find yourself in your bed again. Handy right?
Message.LocalizedString: Death's made a deal with the Wise Old Coot, so if you die you'll just find yourself in your bed again. Handy right?
